data.description: No property on 2-1/2 acres is closer to Silverdale/Bremerton than this one! Single Story RAMBLER just off Holly Road on a dead end street near Wildcat Lake. 3 BR, 1-3/4 Bath surrounded by mature trees & has loads of parking. Freshly painted inside & new lighting keeps things bright! The large living room leads to the decks, separate dining space 'breakfast bar' connects to the kitchen. All appliances stay, including W/D in the oversized 2 car garage. A cozy wood stove makes these cool NW days enjoyable and comfy along with a mini split when AC is needed. The primary bedroom has its own bathroom with a full tub! And either bedroom can work as flex space for an office, studies or sleeping. MOVE-In Ready! Don't miss out! This home is the one!
